Professional Portfolio Website
A modern, responsive portfolio website built with Bootstrap 5, featuring smooth animations and professional design.

File Structure
index.html - Main HTML structure
styles.css - Custom CSS styles and animations
script.js - JavaScript functionality and interactions
Features
Responsive Design: Works on all devices
Smooth Animations: Fade-in effects and hover animations
Modern Navigation: Fixed navbar with smooth scrolling
Professional Layout: Clean, elegant design
Contact Integration: Ready for contact form implementation
Sections
Current Sections
Hero Section: Introduction and call-to-action
About: Professional summary
Experience: Work history
Projects: Portfolio showcase
Skills: Technical expertise
Contact: Contact information
Future Sections (Ready to Add)
Located in HTML as comments:

Professional Development Timeline
Certifications Display
Training Delivered
Detailed Education
Academic Projects
Research Publications
Conference Presentations
Customization Guide
Colors
Edit CSS variables in styles.css:

css
:root {
    --primary-color: #2c3e50;
    --secondary-color: #3498db;
    --accent-color: #e74c3c;
}
Content Updates
Personal Info: Update name, title, and contact details in index.html
Experience: Modify experience cards in the experience section
Projects: Update project cards with your actual projects
Skills: Edit the skills lists to match your expertise
Adding New Sections
Add HTML structure between existing sections
Include appropriate classes for consistency
Update navigation links in the navbar
Add smooth scrolling functionality in script.js
Images
Add profile image in hero section
Include project screenshots in project cards
Optimize images for web (WebP format recommended)
Contact Form
Replace contact section with working form:

Add form HTML structure
Implement form validation in script.js
Connect to backend service or email API
Browser Support
Chrome 90+
Firefox 88+
Safari 14+
Edge 90+
Dependencies
Bootstrap 5.3.0 (CSS/JS)
Bootstrap Icons 1.10.0
Modern browser with ES6 support
Getting Started
Download all files to your web directory
Update personal information in index.html
Customize colors and styling in styles.css
Add your actual content and projects
Test responsiveness on different devices
Performance
Optimized CSS with efficient selectors
Debounced scroll events for smooth performance
Lazy loading ready for images
Minimal JavaScript footprint
SEO Ready
Semantic HTML structure
Meta tags included
Proper heading hierarchy
Alt text placeholders for images
